➜特朗普确诊后首次接受电视采访：我非常强壮，已经停止服药
http://www.sohu.com/a/423690507_260616	31865
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
showVrsPlayer({
bid:'218187228',
width: '500',
height: '375',
